ration-pack-12L-pockets.jpg\" alt=\"USWE Epic Series hydration pack, 12L, inside pocket\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-420x420.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174054/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-12L-pockets-420x420.jpg 420w\"></a></p><p>Both of the larger packs are available in USWE Red or Horizon Blue. The 8L pack weighs 545g and its dimensions are 42x19x12cm. The 8L model goes for $139.95. The 12L EPIC pack hits the scale at 590g, and it measures 48x23x12cm. MSRP is $149.95.</p><figure id=\"attachment_262246\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262246\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider.jpg\" alt=\"USWE Epic Series hydration pack, on rider\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/19174119/USWE-Epic-hydration-pack-rider-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262246\">*Photos c. USWE</figcaption></figure><p>All EPIC Series packs are now available online and at speciality retailers.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.uswe-sports.com/\"><em>uswe-sports.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Steve Fisher","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"88bfc3ae2f47624feedc61bc3aa2d0c3baab3d6d487177a2b3c53ba4bb9ce9bd","category":"Cycling"}